        <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-7be05dc9f0ba468f914028414429cac0" font="|8|0" lineColor="#6A1B9A" fillColor="#D1C4E9">
          <bounds x="1455" y="300" width="350" height="80"/>
          <content>SHARED — AWS Cloud Server hosts the HMS (via HMS Runtime)
for both domains. Per-domain: RFID/door devices (Room Access),
Wi-Fi + Android phones (Daily Briefing).</content>
